For more information, visit the <a href="http://www.raytheon9.org" target="_blank">Raytheon Nine</a> Web site, and watch <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QmTJbEYsN4A" target="_blank">Eamonn McCann speaking about the Raytheon protest</a> in a speech posted at YouTube.
